APEDANICA  (ASOCIACION  PARA LA PREVENCION Y ESTUDIO  DE  DELITOS
ABUSOS Y NEGLIGENCIAS EN INFORMATICA Y COMUNICACIONES AVANZADAS),
Spanish   Legal  Advanced  Communications  and   Computer   Crime
Research Association, has founded a Club of Electronic Signatures
Users in Madrid,  in order to share activities and information in
this field, if possible in Spanish (we are pleased to translate).

CLUB DE USUARIOS APEDANICOS NACIONALES Y TELEMATICOS AVALANTES DE
LAS FIRMAS ELECTRONICAS (CUANTAFE) will organize meetings and any
activity that can help to develop  Public Key Cryptology  markets
and its knowledge.  RSA, El Gamal, Zero Knowledge Proof and other
ideas, algorithms, programs, articles, books,  documentation  and
references will be shared and studied here, in Madrid.

Sponsors are wellcome!

Please do not hesitate to contact me for further information.


